Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:27.98,DtB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,The one who showed up this time sure is pretentious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:34.45,DtB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,According to the Division of Astronomy, the spectrum of the detected star contained characteristics of a Moratorium.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:41.32,DtB-Default,Kouno,0,0,0,,Burned to a crisp, just like the bacon I ate this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:43.87,DtB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,Moratorium, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.20,0:00:45.54,DtB-Default,Saitou,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:51.54,DtB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:55.40,DtB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Why Tahara's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:00.22,DtB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Do you have any particular information on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:11.85,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,When I was a child, Papa told me there was an amulet inside that was protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:25.91,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Information about Tahara's daughter being a contractor or something didn't exist until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:29.05,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Do you know what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:33.33,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Tahara's research was progressing according to his plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.41,0:01:36.79,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,We'll obtain both at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:38.84,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,It's time for work, Ruuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:42.50,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:44.11,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,It isn't me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:46.19,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,It's not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.37,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Meyer & Hilton?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:55.35,DtB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,When the U.K. started mobilizing during the Argentine Coast War,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:59.38,DtB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,{\fscx95}they supplied the country with contractors for artillery purposes, since they were the first company to implement such weaponry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:02.18,DtB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,I haven't heard any good rumors about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:05.49,DtB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Inbreeding in order to mass-produce contractors...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:09.81,DtB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Manufacturing hybrids by breeding distinct supernatural beings...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:13.77,DtB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Experimenting with neurosurgical contract validation on civilians...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:17.07,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,What is their relationship with the Moratorium in question?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:18.38,DtB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:21.42,DtB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,However, around ten years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:25.30,DtB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,a Japanese man was hired as a researcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.28,DtB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,There has been no leakage of details.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:31.60,DtB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Their purpose of entry, the subject of the research,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.09,0:03:34.64,DtB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,and the emergence of the new star...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:36.96,DtB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,There may be some correlation between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:41.20,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Understood. I'll have Saitou and Kouno look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:43.51,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I'm on the trail of the Moratorium.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:45.52,DtB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Hurry, Kirihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:49.51,DtB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,The Moratorium must be apprehended and quarantined at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:52.82,DtB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,They are neither contractors nor Dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:57.52,DtB-Default,Hourai,0,0,0,,Rather, they're defective monsters who merely abuse their powers and have no sense of self-awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:00.36,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:12.79,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an5\c&H030204&\be1\b1\fax0.4\3c&HB9B1AC&\frx6\fry12\frz341.983\move(733,293,734,116)}National\NObservatory{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:23.30,DtB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.80,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Good work, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.80,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,How's the target, Chief Ishizaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:35.52,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Our mediums have tracked it again around Nerima Ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:39.98,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,However, we have only confirmed the tail end of a strong, sentient resonance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:43.95,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,We have suspended further monitoring activities for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:47.88,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,What about the evacuation alert?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:51.57,DtB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,We have already issued one for a five kilometer radius under the pretense of a broken gas line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:07.51,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,It has been a while, Hoshimi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:09.72,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,It's me, Kirihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:23.56,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,The reason why contractors are called contractors in the first place
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:28.17,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,is because they have to go through a mentally exhausting, yet necessary procedure,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:30.98,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,referred to as remuneration, after using their acquired abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:34.96,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,The process of remuneration is deferred for the Moratorium.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:39.45,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,After a period of time, most of them alter their states into that of a Doll,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:41.57,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,much like our mediums.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:49.31,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Unlike standard contractors, the Moratorium cannot control their abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:52.92,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,That's what we're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:59.11,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,To be honest, the Observatory doesn't know any more than what the people from External Affairs do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:02.10,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Moratorium sightings are few and far between.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:04.00,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:09.11,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Its pulse seems a little unstable this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:12.33,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Long story short, there's no telling what it'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:19.86,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,There you go again, raising your brow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:24.70,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,You're not young anymore, so be careful or those wrinkles will become permanent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:28.29,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,You're as old as I am. You're not in a position to say that to me, Kanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:33.51,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me. I don't take life seriously enough to develop wrinkles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:38.76,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,You haven't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:41.30,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Neither have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:46.52,DtB-Default,Announcement,0,0,0,,To all residents: please proceed to your designated evacuation areas at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:49.27,DtB-Default,Announcement,0,0,0,,This area is extremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:56.24,DtB-Default,Announcement,0,0,0,,{\an8}Refrain from using vehicles, do not carry any luggage, and proceed swiftly without panicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:56.65,DtB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.32,DtB-Default,Announcement,0,0,0,,{\an8}I repeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:07:01.52,DtB-Default,Announcement,0,0,0,,{\an8}To all residents: please proceed to your designated evacuation areas at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:02.70,DtB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,What are you doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:04.96,DtB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry, you'll be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.38,DtB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,The gas lines are broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:10.15,DtB-Default,Yuka Dad,0,0,0,,Yuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:13.35,DtB-Default,Yuka Dad,0,0,0,,Is she a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:14.70,DtB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:20.12,DtB-Default,Yuka Dad,0,0,0,,It's all right, you don't have to be scared. Let's evacuate together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.99,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,No, don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.85,DtB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,He's my father, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:28.11,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:29.29,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:30.11,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:32.92,DtB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:33.86,DtB-Default,Yuka Dad,0,0,0,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:37.36,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:43.41,DtB-Default,Yuka,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:44.17,DtB-Default,Yuka Dad,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.10,0:08:03.14,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.18,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:14.97,DtB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:17.74,DtB-Default,Mayu,0,0,0,,Target sighted at Nakano Ward, Maruyamakita.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:20.05,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Do not antagonize the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:21.45,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Wait for the Special Forces to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:29.60,DtB-Default,Cop,0,0,0,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.54,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an2\fscy140\fscx80\pos(885,581)}Episode Four
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.54,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(1174,682)}A New Star Shines in the Dawn Sky... \N(Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:19.61,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Dr. Tahara, you're so mean-spirited.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:22.59,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Everything has gone according to your plans, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:25.76,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,I'm talking about your research on suppressing contractors from awakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:33.24,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,In any case, I didn't realize your daughter was the subject of your experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:38.53,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Of course, I could personally make a trip to your factory, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:43.04,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,I would prefer to avoid further casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:45.90,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,I will release your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.71,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,You have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:54.18,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Um... His hair is messy and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:09:59.96,DtB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:02.21,DtB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,Did you use your daughter as a sample for your experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.83,DtB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,What did you do to your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:10.28,DtB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,What did you plant in Mai's wrist?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:17.27,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've heard about it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:22.56,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I was the sole survivor of the First Gate Reconnaissance Troop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:29.21,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I had brought a certain material back with me at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:35.59,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,There was a possibility I could block the activation of a contractor's abilities by implanting it inside their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:42.88,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I discovered it two years after being employed by Meyer & Hilton.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:46.65,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Around the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:10:59.16,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,M-Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:01.13,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:07.77,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:14.89,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,The way contractors were regarded by the public...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.93,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,You know what I'm talking about, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:28.66,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,By implanting the unknown material found within the gate into Mai's wrist...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:32.15,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I attempted to prevent the activation of her abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:34.20,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I was grasping at straws.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:41.30,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,No, straws isn't correct. What I was grasping at were seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:46.73,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,In retrospect, those seeds may have contained the curse of the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:49.95,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,It might have been punishment for treading inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:54.13,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,The seed implanted in Mai will eventually deteriorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:57.60,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,After that happens, her ability will be awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:00.49,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,As I continued my research,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:05.81,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I came to the conclusion that complete suppression would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:11.93,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Furthermore, the host body of the implanted seed would transform into a Moratorium.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:14.94,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,There's no telling when its curse will subside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:23.24,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,With my own hands, I turned my daughter into a monster that can't even become a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:27.90,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I destroyed whatever data remained.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:32.92,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I erased Mai's memories using the M.E. and left the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:36.30,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I couldn't afford to let them find out about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:39.73,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I didn't want her to become the subject of an actual experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:43.89,DtB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,So you abandoned everything you had and ran off to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:50.24,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Didn't I just say it's impossible to suppress the activation of the contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:54.65,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Are you saying I should continue this meaningless experiment on my child?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:01.68,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I was able to bring back two seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:03.61,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,One is in Mai's wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.31,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,The other...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:10.62,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,If the seed within Mai began to deteriorate to the point of vanishing entirely...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:14.42,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,If I could cultivate the seed and implant it again,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:21.76,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I'd be able to suppress the Moratorium's instinctual behavior forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:28.93,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,The only time I had peace of mind was when I watered this pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:32.81,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,However, time stopped this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:36.35,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,It didn't bear any seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:40.19,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I was frightened...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:43.73,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Frightened of witnessing the result of my sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:48.87,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,If I knew this was going to happen, she would have been better off as a contractor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:52.66,DtB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,You're confessing your sins to the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:56.97,DtB-Default,Li,0,0,0,,You deserve to be confined inside this room forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:08.40,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,It was supposed to bear lots of fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:10.05,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:16.80,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Lots and lots of seeds for your amulet were supposed to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:29.25,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,And the eyebrow is bushy with spots of whiskers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:32.94,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Finally here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:35.52,DtB-Default,Ruuko,0,0,0,,Yeah, some dog wandered in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:46.59,DtB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:53.68,DtB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Koutou Ward, Shinonome warehouse district.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:12.61,DtB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,A contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:17.74,DtB-Default,Ruuko,0,0,0,,It looks like you and I are alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:35.80,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,That's as far as you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:42.35,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Or do you not care about what happens to Tahara's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:48.61,DtB-Default,Ruuko,0,0,0,,You should have retrieved the daughter instead of going after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:53.48,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Really, you hired a strange contractor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:55.00,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Dr. Tahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.34,0:16:01.20,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Return my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:04.96,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,In that case, are you willing to lend us a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:08.35,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I will not return to your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:12.50,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I brought referential material from my research instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:14.72,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:16.43,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,My daughter comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:22.18,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Hey, your beloved papa has come to pick you up, Mai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:24.93,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,No, I don't know... that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:33.82,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:38.99,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,H-Hurry up and hand over the documents!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.68,0:16:46.98,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:48.50,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,References.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.52,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,What are you trying to pull?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:51.94,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Hand over the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:54.76,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,This is all that's left of my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:02.89,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,No! No! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:07.54,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,No, Mai's papa is more handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:09.23,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,He's stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:11.44,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,No, your father is a horrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:15.06,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,He's not horrible! He tells me many, many stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:17.31,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,He protects Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:20.46,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Mai likes Papa very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:26.56,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Papa likes you very much, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:29.26,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:31.13,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:45.49,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Forget about him! Get a hold of the sample!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:18:00.07,DtB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Smiles don't belong on people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:07.84,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:09.37,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:14.19,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,My work... is finally done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.02,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:19.92,DtB-Default,Kouzou,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.73,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Welcome back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:25.81,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:36.03,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,Wait... It was Ruuko who did it, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:38.07,DtB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Stop, Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:42.15,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:45.78,DtB-Default,Kenneth,0,0,0,,D-Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:15.30,DtB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Her remuneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:17.78,DtB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Did she become a contractor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.42,DtB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,A Moratorium?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:21.42,DtB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,The probability is practically zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:24.28,DtB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Geez, strange things sure do happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:27.07,DtB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I'll forget about what happened to Tahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:29.74,DtB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I have something much more interesting instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:39.25,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,I feel as if I've killed many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:41.57,DtB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Don't be so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:44.49,DtB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Contractors exist solely to kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.56,DtB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I guess you're not depressed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.72,DtB-Default,Mai,0,0,0,,Where am I going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:56.39,DtB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Heaven, although it'll be a long journey by ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:07.82,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,When we arrived at the scene, the Moratorium's location
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:11.83,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,and Messier code BK201, which was flickering along with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:13.34,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,could not be traced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:20.66,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,Eventually, investigation of Case Code 1032 was transferred away from the Department of Intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:25.07,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,To this day, no information of any significance has surfaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:29.00,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,However, one thing's for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:37.10,DtB-Default,Misaki,0,0,0,,The star that appeared that day has yet to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:46.13,DtB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The being who came from Eastern Europe was a woman once referred to as a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.13,0:20:50.89,DtB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Her blank eyes show a pale, cold light full of loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:56.54,DtB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,A breath escapes from lips that remain sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:21:00.49,DtB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Is it the devil's whisper or a sigh of relief?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:05.01,DtB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The catastrophic wind was never to blow again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:08.43,DtB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,And the trap was set.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:09.36,Title,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hededed&}Episode Five Red Giant over Eastern Europe (Part One)